title: Ep. 107 - Auxiliary To The Exorcist
description: Todd shares an interesting conversation that he had with the Auxiliary to the Exorcist assigned to the Archdiocese of Indianapolis. The crew also discussed prison life in other countries, Gump's immigration status, Labradoodles, Nicolas Cage, cat allergies, haunted house murders and more...
